remarks: Commutation of restricted universal quantifiers.  Note that ` x ` and ` y ` need not be distinct (this makes the proof longer).  (Contributed by NM, 24-Nov-1994.)  (Proof shortened by Mario Carneiro, 17-Oct-2016.)
statement:
ralcom2 $p |- ( A. x e. A A. y e. A ph -> A. y e. A A. x e. A ph ) $.
$d A x $.
$d A y $.
